### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → PLAN GENERATION CONTEXTS — /api/v1/admin/plan-contexts
### ============================================================================

### List plan generation contexts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plan-contexts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Upload plan generation context (multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plan-contexts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=context-boundary

--context-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

WHO Malaria Guidelines 2025
--context-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="malaria-guidelines-2025.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./malaria-guidelines-2025.pdf
--context-boundary--

### Set context active/inactive
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plan-contexts/{{planContextId}}/active?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete plan context
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plan-contexts/{{planContextId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
